{
  "stem": "22004.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So, and I went with him to the office and I explained what he was saying to the-- to the Russians, to the Russian officers.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then it was there-- I was there until it started to get warmer.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the mines started to go off.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I wasn't there already.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was trying to talk to the officer to send us-- to get us out from there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they-- he said to me that the commissar is going to send us to in the back in Russia.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In Russia, there were [INAUDIBLE] there, to make him-- to make him nice shoes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I was-- my feet was swollen like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Swollen and hunger.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, my brother got a problem with his foot, they have to put them out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I have to carry him on my back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we went-- he said, I can't send you out from here until you get it from a doctor, a paper.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You can do nothing anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You are sick.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So, and the doctor was a good friend of ours-- a Jewish guy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was not even a doctor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was-- he was running the SS-- the SS-- a bath, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I'm sorry?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They're taking baths, you know, showers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was in charge of the place--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was in charge for the doctor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he was not a doctor, still, but he was in charge.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyway, I went to him and I told him, we have to get out of here because we are frozen and swollen.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he said, well, he wants something from us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because I got a box with leather, with all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I gave it and he gave us a paper.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
